SecureTrading,is,a,UK,based,online,secure,payment,service,that,processes,billions,of,dollars,annually,The,SecureTrading,API,allows,users,to,automate,refunds,and,authorization,reversals,and,control,settlement,schedules,Users,can,also,integrate,a,payment,service,into,back,office,or,legacy,system,The,API,uses,REST,protocols,and,returns,XML